rows.label: tlk45320651_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I went to Trigo to visit
Professor Tatezo again.

rows.label: tlk45320651_04_msg0002
rows.name:
It was a more fruitful trip than
last time, that's for sure!

rows.label: tlk45320651_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I actually managed to score
9,840 points in Tiger! Tiger!

rows.label: tlk45320651_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Smashed my old high score,
don't you know!

rows.label: tlk45320651_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Though I still didn't manage to
beat Professor Tatezo himself...

rows.label: tlk45320651_04_msg0006
rows.name:
I think I'm going to have a word
with Central R&D.

rows.label: tlk45320651_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Tell them to stop working on artificial
Blades for now, and try to make a real
masterpiece like Tiger! Tiger!
